Package: Rcaline
Type: Package
Title: Rcaline - Gaussian dispersion modeling tools based on CALINE
Version: 0.8
Date: 2011-01-11
Author: David Holstius
Maintainer: David Holstius <david.holstius@berkeley.edu>
Depends: 
Suggests: sp, rgdal, spatstat, maptools
Description: Predicts steady-state aerosol concentrations downwind from mobile emission sources (e.g., highway traffic) represented as segments. Uses the CALINE3 Gaussian dispersion model.
License: BSD
Copyright: Copyright (c) 2010 The Regents of the University of California
LazyLoad: yes
References: Benson, P. (1979) CALINE-3: A versatile dispersion model for predicting air pollution levels near highways and urban streets. Federal Highway Authority report FHWA/CA/TL-79/23, California DOT, Sacramento (1979).
